Day 20 — Jun 29 — Ingress + Nginx Controller
Study

Ingress = L7 routing (host/path-based). Needs an Ingress Controller (nginx, traefik, istio).
TLS termination at ingress.
IngressClass.
Hands-On

# minikube
minikube addons enable ingress

# Apply ingress
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata: {name: web-ing}
spec:
  ingressClassName: nginx
  rules:
  - host: web.local
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: Prefix
        backend: {service: {name: web, port: {number: 80}}}

echo "$(minikube ip) web.local" | sudo tee -a /etc/hosts
curl http://web.local

